Quero começar lembrando que tive que se tornar um adulto aos 9 anos quando meus pais se separaram.
texto_traduzido:
The month of September starts and two years later I have the courage to speak openly on a social network about what I went through two years ago because of depression.
I want to start by remembering that I had to become an adult at 9 when my parents separated.
